rporate income advisors llc cole corporate income advisors ii llc cole reit advisors v llc and cole capital advisors inc since june  he has been chief executive officer and president of cole income nav strategy ccpt v and ccit ii since june  he has extensive experience growing and creating shareholder value in the commercial real estate industry mr rufrano served as the chief executive officer and chairman of oconnor capital partners since november   he was a partner and cofounder at the oconnor group inc from  to march  and had served as its president and chief operating officer mr rufrano was among the founders of oconnor capital partners in  he served as chairman and chief executive officer of oconnor capital partners from november  to march  he served as the chief executive officer of cushman  wakefield ltd since march  mr rufrano served as the chief executive officer and president at cushman  wakefield inc from march  to june  and as its director until june  he served as the chief executive officer at centro retail group since january  mr rufrano served as the chief executive officer at centro properties group limited since january  until february   he served as the chief executive officer of us operations at centro properties group limited since july   until february  mr rufrano served as the chief executive officer at new plan excel realty trust inc from february  to  as its president from february  to march  and had also served as its director since  he had joined new plan excel realty trust inc in february  mr rufrano served as the chief executive officer at brixmor llc previously known as centro np llc from february  to  and had also served as its director he served as the chief executive officer at cnpr limited from january  to february   and as the chief executive officer of us from april  to  mr rufrano served as the chief executive officer at centro mcs manager limited at federation limited since january  he served as president and chief operating offi